{
  "page": "Ermesande Hayford",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hayford\" title=\"House Hayford\"><img alt=\"House Hayford.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Hayford.svg/50px-House_Hayford.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Hayford.svg/75px-House_Hayford.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/House_Hayford.svg/100px-House_Hayford.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Ermesande Hayford</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/50px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/75px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/100px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Tyrek_Lannister_and_baby_Ermesande_Hayford_by_Amuelia.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tyrek Lannister and baby Ermesande Hayford by Amuelia.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Tyrek_Lannister_and_baby_Ermesande_Hayford_by_Amuelia.jpg/350px-Tyrek_Lannister_and_baby_Ermesande_Hayford_by_Amuelia.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Tyrek_Lannister_and_baby_Ermesande_Hayford_by_Amuelia.jpg/525px-Tyrek_Lannister_and_baby_Ermesande_Hayford_by_Amuelia.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e6/Tyrek_Lannister_and_baby_Ermesande_Hayford_by_Amuelia.jpg/700px-Tyrek_Lannister_and_baby_Ermesande_Hayford_by_Amuelia.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Ermesande Hayford and her husband, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrek_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrek Lannister\">Tyrek Lannister</a>, by Amuelia ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Hayford\" title=\"Lord of Hayford\">Lady of Hayford</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafermesande_hayford.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafermesande_hayford.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hayford\" title=\"House Hayford\">House Hayford</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafermesande_hayford.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafermesande_hayford.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrek_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrek Lannister\">Tyrek Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ermesande Hayford</b> is the Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Hayford\" title=\"Hayford\">Hayford</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hayford\" title=\"House Hayford\">House Hayford</a>, a noble house of the <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">crownlands</a>. She is still a baby<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and is the last of her line.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ermesande_Hayford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ermesande_Hayford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lady Ermesande attends the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_on_King_Joffrey%27s_name_day\" title=\"Tourney on King Joffrey&#39;s name day\">tourney on King Joffrey's name day</a> with her <a href=\"/index.php/Wet_nurse\" title=\"Wet nurse\">wet nurse</a>. She is rumored to soon wed one of Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a>'s cousins, so the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a> might claim her lands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ermesande is <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Tyrek_Lannister_and_Ermesande_Hayford\" title=\"Wedding of Tyrek Lannister and Ermesande Hayford\">married</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrek_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrek Lannister\">Tyrek Lannister</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> but he disappears soon after during the <a href=\"/index.php/Riots_in_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Riots in King&#39;s Landing\">riots in King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ermesande_Hayford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ermesande nurses during <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Tyrion_Lannister_and_Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Wedding of Tyrion Lannister and Sansa Stark\">the wedding</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ermesande_Hayford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wearing a <a href=\"/index.php/Jade\" title=\"Jade\">jade</a>-decorated gown, Ermesande is brought before Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> and his retinue when their host stops at <a href=\"/index.php/Hayford\" title=\"Hayford\">Hayford</a> while en route to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>. The crying girl is taken to bed by her wet nurse, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ermesande_Hayford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrek_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrek Lannister\">Tyrek</a> was the son of his late <a href=\"/index.php/Tygett_Lannister\" title=\"Tygett Lannister\">Uncle Tygett</a>, a boy of thirteen. He had vanished in <a href=\"/index.php/Riots_in_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Riots in King&#39;s Landing\">the riot</a>, not long after <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Tyrek_Lannister_and_Ermesande_Hayford\" title=\"Wedding of Tyrek Lannister and Ermesande Hayford\">wedding</a> the Lady Ermesande, a suckling babe who happened to be the last surviving heir of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hayford\" title=\"House Hayford\">House Hayford</a>. And likely the first bride in the history of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> to be widowed before she was weaned.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>My fealty's owed to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hayford\" title=\"House Hayford\">House Hayford</a>, and Lady Ermesande bends her little knee at <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, or will when she's old enough to walk.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Roger_Hogg\" title=\"Roger Hogg\">Roger Hogg</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ermesande_Hayford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafermesande_hayford.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafermesande_hayford.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafermesande_hayford.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\